channel.title: Hi, I'm Daren CEO of Benchmark
channel.description:
Hey there! I’m Daren .
I’ve been a career creative for over 15 years, and have spent much of that time building my own business up to six figures in revenue, and helping artists and creatives do the same.
I'm now working on a Business Dashboard For Founders And Creators: benchmark.app!
Glad to be part of your community!
